to be comfortable and inviting
and inclusive because there's

00:21:26.540 --> 00:21:29.800 align:middle line:84%
a lot of us who don't feel
that way in yoga spaces.

00:21:29.800 --> 00:21:32.400 align:middle line:84%
So I wanted to create a space
that said yes, you are welcome

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:35.940 align:middle line:84%
here no matter who you are,
no matter what you look

00:21:35.940 --> 00:21:38.987 align:middle line:84%
like, no matter who you
love, no matter what

00:21:38.987 --> 00:21:40.070 align:middle line:90%
your gender assignment is.

00:21:40.070 --> 00:21:42.840 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to make sure there was
a place where everybody that's

00:21:42.840 --> 00:21:48.100 align:middle line:84%
been traditionally pushed to the
margins in mainstream culture

00:21:48.100 --> 00:21:50.270 align:middle line:84%
could feel that this
was a place for them.

00:21:50.270 --> 00:21:51.900 align:middle line:84%
And we've seen that
in yoga culture

00:21:51.900 --> 00:21:56.080 align:middle line:84%
as well with what the
current aesthetic of yoga is.

00:21:56.080 --> 00:21:58.230 align:middle line:84%
So I wanted to really
shift that consciousness

00:21:58.230 --> 00:22:00.460 align:middle line:84%
and shift that
dynamic and make sure

00:22:00.460 --> 00:22:02.960 align:middle line:84%
that people understood
that yoga is in all of us

00:22:02.960 --> 00:22:04.750 align:middle line:90%
and is for all of us.

00:22:04.750 --> 00:22:06.720 align:middle line:84%
And everybody has just
as much of a right

00:22:06.720 --> 00:22:08.880 align:middle line:84%
to be on the yoga
mat as anybody else.

00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:10.420 align:middle line:84%
And there's a whole
group of people

00:22:10.420 --> 00:22:14.640 align:middle line:84%
who really need the practice
who aren't getting the practice.

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:17.260 align:middle line:84%
And I needed to figure out
how to get the practice

00:22:17.260 --> 00:22:19.950 align:middle line:84%
to those people, which is
why I became a teacher,

00:22:19.950 --> 00:22:23.650 align:middle line:84%
