culturally sensitive

00:22:30.770 --> 00:22:34.730 align:middle line:84%
and we could create a really
inclusive and diverse space

00:22:34.730 --> 00:22:37.440 align:middle line:84%
for all people to come
and practice yoga.

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:39.160 align:middle line:90%
How can we decolonize yoga?

00:22:39.160 --> 00:22:41.120 align:middle line:84%
First of all, I think
we need to pull yoga out

00:22:41.120 --> 00:22:44.710 align:middle line:84%
of the expensive, exclusive
clubs called yoga studios

00:22:44.710 --> 00:22:47.890 align:middle line:84%
and offer them in more
accessible areas like community

00:22:47.890 --> 00:22:53.020 align:middle line:84%
centers, even just public
spaces, even the park.

00:22:53.020 --> 00:22:57.020 align:middle line:84%
I also think that yoga
should be funded or actually

00:22:57.020 --> 00:22:58.710 align:middle line:84%
picked up by public
health because it

00:22:58.710 --> 00:23:03.070 align:middle line:84%
has a lot of benefits for people
who are suffering with stress,

00:23:03.070 --> 00:23:06.980 align:middle line:84%
depression, anxiety, high blood
pressure, emotional issues.

00:23:06.980 --> 00:23:09.840 align:middle line:84%
So I really think if it became
more of a public platform,

00:23:09.840 --> 00:23:12.290 align:middle line:84%
it would be accessible
to more communities.

00:23:12.290 --> 00:23:15.820 align:middle line:84%
I also think we need to
acknowledge and recognize

00:23:15.820 --> 00:23:20.560 align:middle line:84%
that we are scrubbing current
yoga of its ethnic origins.

00:23:20.560 --> 00:23:25.100 align:middle line:84%
And we do a lot of that
when we appropriate culture.

00:23:25.100 --> 00:23:28.440 align:middle line:84%
And we remove their cultural
influence on something.

00:23:28.440 --> 00:23:31.070 align:middle line:84%
So I think it's really
important that as yoga teachers

00:23:31.070 --> 00:23:34.150 align:middle line:84%
and practitioners,
we acknowledge where

00:23:34.150 --> 00:23:37.000 align:middle line:84%
this practice comes from
and we show gratitude

00:23:37.000 --> 00:23:41.220 align:middle line:84%
that it's not this diluted,
washed-out commodity that North

00:23:41.220 --> 00:23:43.970 align:middle line:84%
America has created
in its image,

00:23:43.970 --> 00:23:46.150 align:middle line:84%
that we're not here
for a good stretch,

00:23:46.150 --> 00:23:50.620 align:middle line:84%
