primarily for exercise.

00:23:50.620 --> 00:23:52.420 align:middle line:84%
We're here for
spiritual enlightenment.

00:23:52.420 --> 00:23:56.980 align:middle line:84%
And I think that would be a
big part of decolonizing yoga.

